\c 18
\s UJetro uhambela uMozisi
\p
\v 1 Kwathi uJetro\x + 2.18. 3.1.\x* umpristi weMidiyani\x + 18.12. 2.16.\x*, uyisezala kaMozisi, esezwile konke uNkulunkulu ayemenzele khona uMozisi loIsrayeli isizwe sakhe, ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimkhuphile uIsrayeli eGibhithe,
\v 2 uJetro uyisezala kaMozisi wathatha uZipora umkaMozisi emva kokumbuyisela kwakhe\x + 4.26.\x*,
\v 3 kanye lamadodana akhe amabili\x + Seb. 7.29.\x*; obizo lenye lalinguGereshoma, ngoba wathi: Ngangingowemzini elizweni lemzini;
\v 4 lebizo lenye linguEliyezeri, ngoba uNkulunkulu kababa wayelusizo lwami, wangikhulula enkembeni kaFaro\x + Gen. 4.25; 26.7; 32.30; 41.51,52. 2 Sam. 9.11; 18.23. Jobe 32.17. Jer. 4.31; 6.17; 20.10. Mark. 6.9. Seb. 1.4.\x*.
\v 5 UJetro uyisezala kaMozisi wasesiza lamadodana akhe lomkakhe kuMozisi enkangala, entabeni kaNkulunkulu\x + 3.1,12.\x* lapho ayemise khona inkamba.
\v 6 Wasesithi kuMozisi: Mina, uyihlozala, uJetro, ngiza kuwe lomkakho lamadodana akhe amabili elaye.
\v 7 UMozisi wasephuma ukumhlangabeza uyisezala\x + Gen. 14.17; 18.2; 19.1. 1 Kho. 2.19.\x*, wakhothama, wamanga\x + Gen. 29.13; 33.4. 2 Sam. 19.39.\x*. Basebebuzana impilakahle; bangena ethenteni.
\v 8 UMozisi wasemlandisela uyisezala ngakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayikwenzile kuFaro lakumaGibhithe ngenxa kaIsrayeli, yonke inhlupheko eyabehlela endleleni, lokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* yayibakhulule.
\v 9 UJetro wasethokoza ngakho konke okuhle iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayikwenzele uIsrayeli\x + Jobe 3.6.\x*, ukuthi yayimkhulule esandleni samaGibhithe.
\v 10 UJetro wasesithi: Ibusisiwe iN\nd kosi\x + Gen. 14.20. 2 Sam. 18.28. Luka 1.68.\x*\nd* elikhulule esandleni samaGibhithe lesandleni sikaFaro; eyakhulula lesisizwe ngaphansi kwesandla samaGibhithe.
\v 11 Khathesi sengisazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* inkulu kulabo bonke onkulunkulu, ngoba endabeni\x + 1.10,16,22; 5.2,7; 14.18.\x* abazigabisa ngayo yayiphezu kwabo\x + Neh. 9.10,16,29. Hlab. 119.21. Luka 1.51.\x*.
\v 12 UJetro uyisezala kaMozisi wasethathela uNkulunkulu umnikelo wokutshiswa lemihlatshelo; kwasekusiza uAroni labo bonke abadala bakoIsrayeli ukudla isinkwa loyisezala kaMozisi phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 12.7. 14.26. 1 Lan. 29.21,22. Gen. 31.54. 24.11.\x*.
\s Ukubekwa kwabahluleli
\p
\v 13 Kwasekusithi kusisa uMozisi wahlala ukwahlulela abantu; njalo abantu bema phambi kukaMozisi kusukela ekuseni kwaze kwahlwa.
\v 14 Kwathi lapho uyisezala kaMozisi esekubonile konke akwenzela abantu wathi: Iyini linto oyenza ebantwini? Uhlalelani wedwa, labantu bonke bemi kuwe kusukela ekuseni kuze kuhlwe?
\v 15 UMozisi wasesithi kuyisezala: Ngoba abantu beza kimi ukubuza kuNkulunkulu\x + Levi 24.12. Nani 15.34.\x*.
\v 16 Nxa belendaba\x + 23.7. 24.14. Dute. 17.8. 2 Sam. 15.2,3. 1 Kor. 6.1.\x*, beza kimi, njalo ngahlulele phakathi komuntu lomakhelwane wakhe, ngi\add b\add*azise izimiso zikaNkulunkulu lemithetho yakhe\x + Levi 24.15. Nani 15.35; 27.6; 36.6.\x*.
\v 17 Uyisezala kaMozisi wasesithi kuye: Into oyenzayo kayinhle.
\v 18 Isibili uzazidlakaza, wena-ke lalababantu abalawe; ngoba linto inzima kakhulu kuwe, kawulakukwenza wedwa\x + Nani 11.14,17. Dute. 1.9,12.\x*.
\v 19 Khathesi lalela ilizwi lami; ngizakweluleka, njalo uNkulunkulu abe lawe\x + 3.12.\x*. Wena kawube ngowabantu phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + 4.16. 20.19. Dute. 5.5.\x*, wena ulethe izindaba kuNkulunkulu\x + Nani 27.5.\x*,
\v 20 ubafundise izimiso lemithetho\x + Hlab. 19.11. Hez. 33.3,.\x*, ubazise indlela abamele bahambe ngayo\x + Hlab. 143.8.\x*, lomsebenzi abamele bawenze\x + Dute. 1.18.\x*.
\v 21 Futhi wena ubone phakathi kwabo bonke abantu amadoda alamandla\x + 18.25. Dute. 1.15,16; 16.18. 2 Lan. 19.5-10. Seb. 6.3.\x*, amesabayo uNkulunkulu\x + Gen. 42.18. 2 Sam. 23.3. 2 Lan. 19.9.\x*, amadoda eqiniso\x + Hez. 18.8.\x*, azonda inzuzo engalunganga\x + Dute. 16.19.\x*, uwabeke phezu kwabo, induna zezinkulungwane, induna zamakhulu, induna zamatshumi amahlanu, lenduna zamatshumi;
\v 22 ukuthi zahlulele abantu ngaso sonke isikhathi\x + 18.26.\x*; kodwa kuzakuthi lonke udaba olukhulu zizaluletha kuwe, kodwa lonke udaba oluncinyane zizalwahlulela zona\x + 18.26. Levi 24.11. Nani 15.33. 27.2. 36.1. Dute. 1.17; 17.8.\x*, ukuze kube lula kuwe, njalo zizathwalisana lawe\x + Nani 11.17.\x*.
\v 23 Uba usenza linto, loNkulunkulu ekulawula, uzakuba lamandla okuma\x + 18.18.\x*, njalo labo bonke lababantu bazabuyela endaweni yabo ngokuthula\x + Gen. 18.33; 30.25; 31.55. 2 Sam. 19.39.\x*.
\v 24 UMozisi waselilalela ilizwi likayisezala, wenza konke ayekutshilo.
\v 25 UMozisi wasekhetha amadoda alamandla kuye wonke uIsrayeli\x + Dute. 1.15.\x*, wawabeka inhloko phezu kwabantu, induna zezinkulungwane, induna zamakhulu, induna zamatshumi amahlanu lenduna zamatshumi.
\v 26 Zasezibahlulela abantu ngaso sonke isikhathi\x + Gen. 18.33; 30.25; 31.55; 16.29. 2 Sam. 19.39.\x*; zaletha kuMozisi indaba ezinzima, kodwa lonke udaba oluncinyane zalwahlulela zona.
\p
\v 27 UMozisi wasemyekela wahamba uyisezala; waya elizweni lakibo\x + Nani 10.29,30.\x*.
